{"tid":1892242,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【90後必看】11位日劇女神全盛時期顏值大比拼　哪位才是你最愛？","createTime":"2020-02-22T11:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T13:50:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"74bcd3f79c8593ed654ecd62bb529588baf1d601","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:39:09.000Z","msg":"在90後成長的年代，陪伴我們的是一套又一套的日劇，亦有不少青春無敵的絕世美女冒起，令男生們的「老婆」也換了一個又一個。<br />\n<br />\n到了今天，雖然她們都已年過30，但仍風采依然，並成為一線日劇女神，不過相信當年她們的美貌所帶來的震撼感，會永遠長留於觀眾心中！<br />\n<br />\n近期日本30代女星的全盛時期成為網上熱話，小編收集了不同網民的意見，整合各女神全盛時期的作品，來回味一下她們的絕世神顏吧！（排名不分先後）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/437910/90%E5%BE%8C%E5%BF%85%E7%9C%8B-11%E4%BD%8D%E6%97%A5%E5%8A%87%E5%A5%B3%E7%A5%9E%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%9B%E6%99%82%E6%9C%9F%E9%A1%8F%E5%80%BC%E5%A4%A7%E6%AF%94%E6%8B%BC-%E5%93%AA%E4%BD%8D%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%80%E6%84%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25BD%2590%2F437910%2F90%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25BF%2585%25E7%259C%258B-11%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258A%2587%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%259B%259B%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%25A1%258F%25E5%2580%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25AF%2594%25E6%258B%25BC-%25E5%2593%25AA%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2589%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2584%259B&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdggUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=670cbbe0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/437910/90%E5%BE%8C%E5%BF%85%E7%9C%8B-11%E4%BD%8D%E6%97%A5%E5%8A%87%E5%A5%B3%E7%A5%9E%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%9B%E6%99%82%E6%9C%9F%E9%A1%8F%E5%80%BC%E5%A4%A7%E6%AF%94%E6%8B%BC-%E5%93%AA%E4%BD%8D%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%80%E6%84%9B</a>"},{"pid":"bcf9bb8a456a22dc06bb105f30d398ad5248c6f1","tid":1892242,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:39:35.000Z","msg":"結衣姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a49f9939c39739fbc596777ed5ceffdcc49b767","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:39:36.000Z","msg":"【1】新垣結衣（31歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f826106d92a7657dd647d.jpg/_ZClSISTxa2aOEJ4eqPFQO7e1bOehgHizPhYw8z4WMM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f826106d92a7657dd647d.jpg%2F_ZClSISTxa2aOEJ4eqPFQO7e1bOehgHizPhYw8z4WMM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a38dc0ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：《父女七日變》（2007）、《戀空》（2007）<br />\n<br />\n結衣於2001年起成為女中小學生人氣雜誌《ニコラ》模特兒，2005年正式於日劇《Sh15uya》作為演員出道，同年與長澤雅美合作《東大特訓班》時的黝黑肌膚亦令人印象深刻。<br />\n<br />\n其後於2007年《父女七日變》一劇爆紅，劇中結衣青春活潑的黑長直形象俘虜萬千少男，同年的電影《戀空》令她人氣更上一層樓，從此奠定女神地位，不少人認為當時的結衣是最美的。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;點擊圖片觀看&darr;&darr;&darr;"},{"pid":"2f856f4251ca7b789f6190581fddc00e528304c6","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:39:56.000Z","msg":"【2】堀北真希（31歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f82ff5e00e37651d94acc.jpg/krI5u6VoWho7JeCIT-g-KvTU7Nn6kaPztHYgY7R2IGM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f82ff5e00e37651d94acc.jpg%2FkrI5u6VoWho7JeCIT-g-KvTU7Nn6kaPztHYgY7R2IGM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e0bdcd97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：《野豬大改造》（2005）<br />\n<br />\n說到日劇女神，又怎麼不能提及野豬妹 堀北真希呢？當年於亞視開播的《野豬大改造》，相信也有不少人看過吧！<br />\n<br />\n05年堀北真希於《電車男》飾演主角妹妹後開始嶄露頭角，同年的《野豬大改造》令她人氣急升，07年的《花樣少年少女》令她攀上人氣巔峰，可惜於2016年懷孕後急流勇退，以家庭為重心而暫停藝能活動。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;點擊圖片觀看&darr;&darr;&darr;"},{"pid":"a726db9e23460a992a9946a093378ce7e2029900","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"【3】戶田惠梨香（31歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f835c6f91ff14194bd3ad.jpg/HnQeIYJNqphpogSyX2hSlxcItu9UtgNq3a36z92t-s8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f835c6f91ff14194bd3ad.jpg%2FHnQeIYJNqphpogSyX2hSlxcItu9UtgNq3a36z92t-s8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=8e163b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：《LIAR GAME》（2007）、《死亡筆記》（2006）<br />\n<br />\n與之前兩位一樣，戶田惠梨香也是88年出生，於05年參演《野豬大改造》開始嶄露頭角，06年《死亡筆記》電影版中飾演彌海砂一角令她極速爆紅，07年《LIAR GAME》被認為是戶田的全盛時期。<br />\n<br />\n不過，戶田近年被認為極速劣化，或許與她現時太瘦有關。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;點擊圖片觀看&darr;&darr;&darr;"},{"pid":"4114658c5c5f5d3e70d107ca5bb5f6c965ea7c65","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:40:32.000Z","msg":"【4】長澤雅美（32歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f83f25e00e37651d94ada.jpg/-4AbHZIMpyt6CAVLoA2DHB2XakXNZhH1g6jm94Oo5vc?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f83f25e00e37651d94ada.jpg%2F-4AbHZIMpyt6CAVLoA2DHB2XakXNZhH1g6jm94Oo5vc%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=be8b6784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：《龍櫻》（2005）、《淚光閃閃》（2006）、《求婚大作戰》（2007）<br />\n<br />\n長澤雅美04年憑電影《在世界中心呼喚愛》爆紅，其後05年《東大特訓班》令她人氣急升，07年與山下智久合作的《求婚大作戰》令她登上人氣頂峰，招牌天使笑容融化了無數男生的心。<br />\n<br />\n長澤雅美與新垣結衣當年可算是一時瑜亮，甚至有日本網民評為「瞬間最大風速是長澤雅美；最有安定感則是新垣結衣」。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;點擊圖片觀看&darr;&darr;&darr;"},{"pid":"e5339727bfcd4a46582a0c3235568cbc0fcd43cd","tid":1892242,"uid":74958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"01不了"},{"pid":"afa2f5c93e5216b19f3630998d898b9d98d53f68","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:40:49.000Z","msg":"【5】綾賴遙（34歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f84ad06d92a7657dd64a2.jpg/zn7r0xKHoIq3naYLLfwTBC58zw5DKLBI4NV_xODVf8Q?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f84ad06d92a7657dd64a2.jpg%2Fzn7r0xKHoIq3naYLLfwTBC58zw5DKLBI4NV_xODVf8Q%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=2a30e7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：《在世界中心呼喚愛》（2004）、《我的機械人女友》（2008）<br />\n<br />\n綾賴遙於01年正式作為演員出道，同時亦於寫真界發展，04年與山田孝之合作日劇《在世界中心呼喚愛》爆紅，及後開始以演員為重心，慢慢淡出寫真界，08年電影《我的機械人女友》演出及造型亦令人印象深刻。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;點擊圖片觀看&darr;&darr;&darr;"},{"pid":"8d55d8a157517b11db4d4f5391a147e4b10f6096","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"【6】廣末涼子（39歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f84d55e00e37651d94aea.jpg/wDSa4aEGSS31PBlKpQzxVzl2hdk33HqbKzGSfSsxkn0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f84d55e00e37651d94aea.jpg%2FwDSa4aEGSS31PBlKpQzxVzl2hdk33HqbKzGSfSsxkn0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=97bf7a74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：《沙灘小子》（1997）、《鐵道員》（1999）<br />\n<br />\n廣末涼子可算是日本的短髮女神，由與竹野內豐、反町隆史兩位男神合作《沙灘小子》後爆紅，更於90年代後半引起短髮熱潮。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;點擊圖片觀看&darr;&darr;&darr;"},{"pid":"f707d2ec008aa9cce1a7355ae596da5f22f38784","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:41:28.000Z","msg":"【7】佐佐木希（32歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f85505e00e37651d94aec.jpg/UqPFuD6h3eifsIU7OoXNyekeQVRMuE2r1sXjmNbF45g?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f85505e00e37651d94aec.jpg%2FUqPFuD6h3eifsIU7OoXNyekeQVRMuE2r1sXjmNbF45g%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3d940ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：《出租天使》（2009）<br />\n<br />\n未正式成為演員前的佐佐木希已經是人氣相當高的模特兒，09年主演電影《出租天使》令她人氣更上一層樓，並開始她的演員生涯。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;點擊圖片觀看&darr;&darr;&darr;"},{"pid":"4aceb7a66c2029c1c40c29101868e1ee816f1156","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:41:45.000Z","msg":"【8】澤尻英龍華（33歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f85e6a5af56141f1d4fc2.jpg/4AmfhcZTmarpMjsWBTId0GhBEgKJr5enmZuz7pmbs-4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f85e6a5af56141f1d4fc2.jpg%2F4AmfhcZTmarpMjsWBTId0GhBEgKJr5enmZuz7pmbs-4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=80459758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：《一公升眼淚》（2005）<br />\n<br />\n當年《一公升眼淚》可算是震撼兩岸三地，超凡的演技加上日法混血的無敵外表，可算是前途無可限量。<br />\n<br />\n遺憾的是她紅起來之後接連爆出不少負面新聞，近期也因為吸毒而大有可能終結演藝生涯。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;點擊圖片觀看&darr;&darr;&darr;"},{"pid":"7b38ce2cd16016f702a6d9913edca4dd5b577431","tid":1892242,"uid":342490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:41:46.000Z","msg":"顏你老母咩"},{"pid":"d552886835aea42d8b204aeb02f5b6a807dc08fc","tid":1892242,"uid":210165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:41:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b84bdc9169bfdf5fd855250c4290fde53ee491a","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"【9】北川景子（33歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f866506d92a7657dd64c5.png/2WNRqw3eFYnDkgokdjf2-jCGCcUe3xhB02PkBdNj5AU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f866506d92a7657dd64c5.png%2F2WNRqw3eFYnDkgokdjf2-jCGCcUe3xhB02PkBdNj5AU&h=a1dcb4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：《零秒出手》（2009）<br />\n<br />\n到現時仍是國民女神的北川景子於07年日劇《抹布女孩》中開始爆紅，09年與山下智久合作的《零秒出手》相信是不少90後的青春回憶。除此之外，北川景子亦於06年參演美國電影《狂野時速3》，讓不少外國人也迷上她！<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;點擊圖片觀看&darr;&darr;&darr;"},{"pid":"aebf45134ca168f2934f99fa5352aa1ea7e964e8","tid":1892242,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔係應該80後會清楚啲咩"},{"pid":"46381ba1fc892e38df633cef9d9883c384d41e19","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"【10】石原聰美（33歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f86dc06d92a7657dd64d1.jpg/t8rvTI59LuoAre67benJOWtYt6wKNgRWSIVPQEiFT0A?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f86dc06d92a7657dd64d1.jpg%2Ft8rvTI59LuoAre67benJOWtYt6wKNgRWSIVPQEiFT0A%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e8957c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：不明<br />\n<br />\n顏值隨著年齡上升的人可沒多少，石原聰美就是其中一位，初出道時外表並不突出，甚至被網民嘲她於04年日劇《五個撲水的少年》時十分醜。<br />\n<br />\n不過隨著時間推移，石原也減去臉上的Baby fat，慢慢變成今天的女神，更於16年日劇《校對女王》成為潮流教主，可算至今仍未知她的全盛時期。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;點擊圖片觀看&darr;&darr;&darr;"},{"pid":"4342beaec4e8f9b28701037f5102dced83ffd6da","tid":1892242,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"【11】深田恭子（37歲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e4f870f6f91ff14194bd3f3.jpg/i3zuJ-E3tYis2Huah6mOWA0HAKPIntMUZnShJWZ0oSU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e4f870f6f91ff14194bd3f3.jpg%2Fi3zuJ-E3tYis2Huah6mOWA0HAKPIntMUZnShJWZ0oSU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=43cc00d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期：不明<br />\n<br />\n跟石原聰美一樣，深田恭子也是位凍齡魔女，甚至比初出道時與金城武合作《神啊!請多給我一點時間》（1998）時更美，去年日劇《初戀那一天所讀的故事》更以36歲之齡飾演25歲補習班導師，完全沒違和感。"},{"pid":"087fb0bf6e85dcc2263aa97b78c7bf5c0f00825f","tid":1892242,"uid":253135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:43:21.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"f053ba8b899c69484fde62f0e867f3aee22da605","tid":1892242,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"常盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82385029c6fa3152622ab9702f267f1582ec9fcf","tid":1892242,"uid":15501,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:45:50.000Z","msg":"記得當年舊登長澤同結衣係鬥到難分難解<br />\n<br />\nBTW,我揀長澤"},{"pid":"cab0a2828a3f312517c251c2fbf4a54cdc8db379","tid":1892242,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"夾咗個廣末涼子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宮崎葵